defaultUKMPG pressed strongly for ports to be given high priority for salt supplies not only as an essential part of the nation’s transport infrastructure  network but also because of their role in the distribution of imported salt and grit. The Department of Tra
defaultnsport acted on these concerns and facilitated the distribution of salt and grit supplies to ports which needed them.
